                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-238-off1339 t18290409-238-cd1340"></join>, at St. Botolph Without, Aldgate, 1 watch, value 10l.; 1 watch-chain, value 5l.; 2 seals, value 20s.; 2 rings, value 15s.; 1 watch-key, value 10s.; 1 box, value 5s.; and 1 slide, value 15s., the goods of 
                     
